data <- read.csv("final_data_3.csv")
plot(data$Gross.Domestic.Product..All.Industries,
     data$Count.of.sales,
     xlab = "GDP", 
     ylab = "EV Registration",
     main="EV Registration and GDP in 2017")

plot(data$Mean.Real.Wages,
     data$Count.of.sales,
     xlab = "GDP", 
     ylab = "EV Registration",
     main="EV Registration and GDP in 2017")

     data$Count.of.sales,
     xlab = "GDP", 
     ylab = "EV Registration",
     main="EV Registration and GDP in 2017")

plot(data$Unemployment.Rate,
     data$Count.of.sales,
     xlab = "GDP", 
     ylab = "EV Registration",
     main="EV Registration and GDP in 2017")
